html.htmlText:
Disfruta de Mompox en nuestro acogedor apartamento colonial frente al río Magdalena, en el emblemático punto de la Piedra de Bolívar. Perfecto para 6 a 8 personas, el apartamento tiene 2 habitaciones, cocina equipada, 2 baños con ducha, baño de visitas, barra, comedor y sala cómoda. Relájate y contempla los hermosos amaneceres y atardeceres, disfrutando del aire acondicionado central. Sumérgete en la historia de Mompox y explora sus encantadoras calles.
¡Te esperamos!

section.houseRulesSubtitle: You'll be staying in someone's home, so please treat it with care and respect.

html.htmlText:
✨30 minutes before you arrive you must let us know so that the person in charge will give you the keys.

✨At the time of check-out you must also let us know in advance for the handing over of the keys. 

Water ✨Care: Water in Mompox is a valuable resource, so we ask you to use it consciously.

✨Electricity: There may be occasional outages. To take care of the environment, please turn off the AC when you leave the apartment.

✨Safety: Before leaving, please make sure to lock the door.

✨Drinking water: The tap water is not suitable for consumption, but we offer you some complimentary drinking water bottles. If you need more, you can go to chain stores like D1 and Olympics.
